  "texts": [
    "Specifically, reconstructing images in the near-infrared (NIR) region provides significantly richer information for marine studies (Hu et al. 2023).",
    "However, the application of image reconstruction in agriculture and food sciences is still in the early stages, primarily confined to academic research and pilot projects.",
    "Some challenges need to be addressed, including improving the accuracy of reconstruction algorithms, integrating these systems within existing agricultural and food processing operations, and training staff to effectively use and interpret HSI data.",
    "The application of HSI reconstruction in agri-food products is still relatively new and underexplored, as evidenced by the limited number of studies (Zhao et al. 2020b; Lailyshofa and Saputro 2023; Ahmed et al. 2024b).",
    "Table 2 provides a comprehensive summary of these research efforts, focusing on the application of HSI reconstruction techniques for quality prediction in agri-food products."
  ]
}